Memorial Bridge, people.

05:23.420 --> 05:26.120
Traffic going <i>waaay back
in both directions.</i>

05:26.190 --> 05:27.990
And look out at the corner
of 14th and Elm.

05:28.060 --> 05:29.360
'cause I just
dropped my bagel.

05:30.960 --> 05:33.800
