and refuses to move.

05:33.860 --> 05:35.090
Did you flash
your lights?

05:35.160 --> 05:36.790
Yes.

05:36.870 --> 05:38.840
Well, I'm fresh out
of ideas.

05:38.900 --> 05:39.900
All right!

05:39.970 --> 05:42.840
A chance to catch some rays.

05:42.910 --> 05:44.740
( <i>honking horn )</i>

05:44.810 --> 05:46.240
Come on! Come on!

05:46.310 --> 05:48.780
I got a body in the trunk.

05:48.840 --> 05:50.840
( <i>honking horn )</i>

05:50.910 --> 05:53.810
Mr. Genie, stop fiddling
with the buttons.

05:53.880 --> 05:57.180
Oh! Now you've gotten
chocolate all over everything!

05:57.250 --> 05:58.810
This is Kent Brockman

05:58.890 --> 06:01.360
reporting live from Arnie
Pie's traffic copter

06:01.420 --> 06:03.520
but I can assure you,
this is no mere morning
traffic report.

06:03.590 --> 06:04.560
Hey!

06:04.630 --> 06:05.930
