and stare at the walls.</i>

09:02.500 --> 09:05.200
<i>At Rancho Relaxo,
you're the boss.</i>

09:05.270 --> 09:09.370
<i>Remember, you can't spell
relaxo without relax.</i>

09:12.050 --> 09:13.050
Homer?

09:13.120 --> 09:14.050
