I've seen them naked.

12:15.560 --> 12:16.360
( <i>screams )</i>

12:20.200 --> 12:21.640
Oh, hello

12:21.700 --> 12:23.860
and welcome to Rancho Relaxo.

12:25.840 --> 12:27.180
